===食性===
[[皇家蒂勒爾博物館|皇家蒂勒爾博物館]]恐龍館長韓德森（Donald Henderson）的一份研究指出，根據頜部、頸部及重心力量，鯊齒龍能用頜部舉起最重達424公斤的獵物。<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.inverse.com/article/25258-paleontology-dinosaur-illustrations-paleoart-donald-henderson-tyrrell-museum | title=The Science Behind This Violent Dino Eiffel Tower is Revolutionary}}</ref>

===埋藏學===
SGM-Din 1標本（鯊齒龍頭骨）鼻骨有圓形穿刺傷口、框前緣異常突出。<ref name="path-survey-acro-342">"Acrocanthosauridae fam. nov.," in Molnar (2001). Pg. 342.</ref>

